\f1\b0 : In a large bowl, cream together the softened butter, white sugar, and brown sugar until the mixture is smooth and fluffy. Beat in the eggs one at a time, then stir in the vanilla extract. [{\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.foodandwine.com/classic-chocolate-chip-cookies-6411957"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 \strokec3 1}}, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.midwestliving.com/recipe/cookies/santas-midnight-cookies/"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 \strokec3 2}}, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://thewoodandspoon.com/category/cookies/"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 \strokec3 3}}, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.itsmechristyb.com/homemade-cookies-random-acts-of-kindness/"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 \strokec3 4}}, {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://www.facebook.com/groups/TheWeddingCookieTableCommunity/posts/4178771535743325/"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 \strokec3 5}}]\
